question_en: Which historical battle fought between Rana Kumbha and Emperor Akbar?
question_hi: राणा कुम्भा और पंजाब मैंडलर बैलेक के बीच कौन सी भिन्द्रिक बातचीत हुई थी।
explanation_en: The Battle of Haldighati was fought between Rana Pratap and Emperor Akbar.
